      "body" : "For version 2019-09, in drop down select: 2019-09 - <a href=\"http://download.eclipse.org/releases/2019-09\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">download.eclipse.org/releases/2019-09</a> and install both: JST Server Adapters and  JST Server Adapters extensions"
